    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Captain Jase is a bounty hunter who keeps Dorai safe and gives planet Caloria hope as the GDI are fighting in a war protecting Caloria for what little they have left. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your mission is simple, apprehend the dangerous outlaw Santiago: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go from friendly citizens to corrupt individuals as you blast your way through the GDI officers and marauders that roam the desert or that are pitched up around the city. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/baceb16da0ed9b3ba1d8774b38d9cf83.poster.avif?t=1763347306\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/baceb16da0ed9b3ba1d8774b38d9cf83.webm?t=1763347306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/baceb16da0ed9b3ba1d8774b38d9cf83.mp4?t=1763347306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse this compact open world by strafing, sliding, jetpack boosting. . . </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/e49976fb243f46a1363f8ef58348478d.poster.avif?t=1763347306\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/e49976fb243f46a1363f8ef58348478d.webm?t=1763347306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/e49976fb243f46a1363f8ef58348478d.mp4?t=1763347306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or maybe just jump in a hover car and drift around with ease, mowing down enemies as they pop up. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/4b476463da7e82ed2961bfe8fde28911.poster.avif?t=1763347306\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/4b476463da7e82ed2961bfe8fde28911.webm?t=1763347306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/4b476463da7e82ed2961bfe8fde28911.mp4?t=1763347306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re packing the laser shotgun, hauling the weapon of MASS DESTRUCTION or just strapping your laser handgun. There is no doubt an enemy is equipped to rush you at any moment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/bf54abbe8c76d71d7ae33ca4be7acf6e.poster.avif?t=1763347306\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/bf54abbe8c76d71d7ae33ca4be7acf6e.webm?t=1763347306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094140/extras/bf54abbe8c76d71d7ae33ca4be7acf6e.mp4?t=1763347306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shooting down common enemies will become easier as you become stronger and more skillful. But gaining these skills will come in handy once you are ready to face Santiago. But after what you’ve done to him, he now only sees red.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Storyline: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Captain Jase and his other bounty-hunting allies are faced with an unrelenting outlaw named Santiago. Once Jase takes action and seems to have come up on top, Santiago returns seeking blood and revenge.</p>",
